<h2 id="my-results" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#my-results" class="header-mark"></a>My Results?</h2><figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/devlogs/blast-to-zero/2026-01-13-game-jam-results/images/results_screenshot.png" title="" data-thumbnail="/devlogs/blast-to-zero/2026-01-13-game-jam-results/images/results_screenshot.png" data-sub-html="<h2>Final Results for my submission</h2>"><img  loading="lazy" src=https://rustycruiselabs.github.io/devlogs/blast-to-zero/2026-01-13-game-jam-results/images/results_screenshot.png    height="772" width="649"></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Final Results for my submission</figcaption>
    </figure>
<p>The results are out! Overall, my game ranked <strong>16 out of 103 entries</strong>. Out of all my game jams so far, it seems that I have better reviews in terms of game play, which makes me motivated to continue this game development. The gameplay score was around <strong>3.6</strong> which is probably due to the poor execution in <strong>game feel</strong>, especially in the <strong>lack of target indicators / mini map</strong> which led to players finding it hard to navigate the game.</p>]]></description>
